Comment: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:42.94,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:51.07,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:52.98,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,uh, yeah.
