Comment: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:38.02,TD_Main,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,"Wages"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.44,0:00:01.93,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.56,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:06.70,TD_Main,Nanoko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that during lunch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:10.28,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing is better than kicking some random person!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:14.05,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So you better confirm it with your own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:16.11,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,It's great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.46,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.36,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.62,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you screaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.68,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I need to ask with Valentine's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:30.21,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt hyper-happy kids will listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:31.65,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:33.62,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:36.52,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting like you didn't know! That won't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:36.52,TD_2nd,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:39.68,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to go make out when I'm not looking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:42.31,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Doing stuff like that at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:48.90,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you have to give or get chocolate at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:51.27,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,School's a place to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:53.77,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that from Haruta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:56.30,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:58.02,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you do at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:01:00.03,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it PE?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:02.24,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:04.00,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, Aisaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:06.96,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to the counseling office after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.10,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you still can't tell me your career preferences?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:56.48,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,And Aisaka-san, you still haven't turned in the one from first semester...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.53,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.86,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still working out the details with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.32,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What about your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.49,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,She wants you to go to college, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.66,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:08.91,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,My mother has worked really hard, sometimes too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.58,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want her to suffer on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.50,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I won't go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.08,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.80,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san, why don't you turn it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:22.76,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,My family's rich, so I don't ever have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.97,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to study, nor is there anything I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.68,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.31,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I don't want to go to college...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.27,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:36.52,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that from now on, for the rest of your life, you have to decide on how you want to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.61,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say it was someone else's fault, nor will anyone take responsibility for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.11,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you think about it more carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.70,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.16,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You've never gone against your mother's wishes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.71,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,When you're done filling it out, bring it to the staff room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.63,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,"For the rest of your life"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:03:59.84,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.26,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.59,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.30,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's the career plans form!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.55,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.48,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.94,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can think about my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.70,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even appreciate who I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:30.49,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I've just been ignoring who I am for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.37,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"Why did it become like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.54,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"What should I have done to avoid it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.29,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I want to do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.26,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even think of what I want to do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.59,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I do have something I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.60,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fall in love normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.72,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:55.14,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you don't even have someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.02,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.98,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I may not have one, but what I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:01.36,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,To be born to a normal family, raised as a good girl normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.11,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Meet a guy normally, become friends normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:08.03,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to fall in love normally like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.24,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.95,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, there's no way it'll happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.62,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It was off from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.71,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.33,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's "normal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.79,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? What's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.92,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Who decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:25.76,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you yelling at me all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.85,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.43,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.02,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do about the form?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.10,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.56,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.10,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.74,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.11,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.07,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.08,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I keep saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.24,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:56.29,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima, won't you think it over again—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.67,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:05:59.62,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.84,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.59,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kawashima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.09,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.76,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.38,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.77,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with my shoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.48,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.40,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a shoe fetish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.61,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.37,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:36.29,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to set a long-throw record?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.33,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.71,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.59,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you get called in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:50.01,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,They asked me to be the model for the school uniform in next year's pamphlet, but I turned it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.39,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.01,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your specialty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.47,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do it. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:58.68,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know how long I can stay at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:06:59.60,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.06,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about your fight with Kushieda—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.06,TD_2nd,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:06.53,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like Kushieda Minori can't change my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.86,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:22.29,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I planned to quit school after first semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:25.13,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,The fuss over the stalker had died down too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.13,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You never said a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:30.42,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I thought I'd try staying here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:34.97,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, and the tomorrow after that, if I were here with these guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.18,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.48,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I watched Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.69,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:49.07,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Since I understood her feelings, and if no one else noticed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:53.70,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "I've got to save her."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.32,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:59.79,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Now I think that if I hadn't been here,\N everything would have sorted itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.96,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.17,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.25,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.13,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.63,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really bu—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.51,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's happening with the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.56,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,And my job at the cake shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:23.35,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I had them give me a cute uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.35,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I contacted both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about weird stuff, just get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.57,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.53,TD_Main,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,C-Co-Condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.36,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yacchan's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.87,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji, how's Yacchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.29,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.54,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:47.33,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was so surprised when I saw her faint through my window.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:48.88,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.96,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.76,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go buy something that Yasuko can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.22,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.51,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What about your coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.64,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.78,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have your wallet, your keys, or your cell phone! Not to mention your shopping bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.78,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.99,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and put this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.54,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you, what's with that get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.38,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.80,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No way, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.26,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:36.93,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.89,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:39.97,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:41.60,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.39,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.10,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.43,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting really weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.60,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:47.94,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.99,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.70,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me, Yasuko fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.45,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.45,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one to blame. {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.29,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.45,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,She has anemia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.29,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's a health problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.46,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.46,TD_2nd,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,If I had my act together...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:13.09,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko would have believed that I could really do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.80,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,She would have relied on me more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.38,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,And then it wouldn't have turned out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.30,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.27,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:39.82,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What... Should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:39.82,TD_2nd,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.54,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's... Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:46.79,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.54,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.83,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.17,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Because Yacchan is an amazing mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.85,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.23,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.27,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.06,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.11,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I have somewhere I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.49,TD_Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That puts me in a tough spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:24.32,TD_Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow and the day after are really busy because of Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.83,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but she really can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.25,TD_Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can find anyone else now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.41,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.96,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.63,TD_Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.72,TD_Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That'd really help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.72,TD_2nd,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.34,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:46.76,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do something for Yacchan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.52,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:57.07,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yacchan got fired from her job at the cake shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:57.90,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.82,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, it happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.95,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find another good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.66,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be comforted?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.04,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,W-Welc... {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.25,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,...come! {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.04,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,W-Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.75,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not selling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:22.34,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You need to say it louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:25.39,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're already at a disadvantage with your not-made-for-advertising face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.43,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.76,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really are working!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.31,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.43,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What, it's you—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.85,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta-kun, which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:40.48,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,They say if you ask for a big one at times like these, bad things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.44,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.36,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.41,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.95,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,T-That'll be 580 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:50.24,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You have a big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:53.75,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my sister, she's my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.88,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.84,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it kinda cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.84,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go somewhere warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.21,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.21,TD_2nd,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.59,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,The world is really twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.72,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Noto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.72,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:10.64,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,No reason, I just happened to pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.85,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, did anyone else come by?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:17.06,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,Like Ami-chan or Nanako-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara hasn't come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:19.86,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.27,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:26.36,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,I just, see, I was just wondering if Kihara was going to make a big fuss and give Kitamura chocolate or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.28,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,And then, how was it going...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.57,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:32.99,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. But Taiga, you care about it, right? About "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:33.95,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.25,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:39.38,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you care about Kihara Maya giving chocolate to Kitamura-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.46,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.55,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:51.72,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's one of those things you realize when you're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:48.97,TD_2nd,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.72,TD_2nd,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.22,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:57.35,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's not strange at all. It's a perfectly natural thing... A perfectly natural thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.52,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,A boy's stamen and a girl's pistil...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:00.31,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.77,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.24,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.36,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.49,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep messing around, we'll get yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.91,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped then. {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.37,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's time to summon our lethal weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.67,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You're not by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:20.63,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.92,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, since you came all the way here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.59,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Stupid Chihuahua, I'll give you this one. So hold it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.05,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.55,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me involved in weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.05,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan is beautiful, so I stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.35,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, Stupid Chihuahua, you're really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.51,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You really stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:39.85,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So take this and try saying, "I really love the chocolate here," in a really loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:40.94,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.02,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to promote it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.07,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.73,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do something so dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.40,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Stupid Chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.07,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.70,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you buy one with your own money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.70,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Then you could give it to Minorin and make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:56.37,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was really watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:15:00.87,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You want to make up with Minorin, but you can't do it correctly, the delicate Chihuahua's shaking heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:01.75,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:02.75,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:06.38,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If it's too hard for you, I can call Minorin for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.55,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine's came around with great timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.05,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.47,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Kawashima Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.68,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.76,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute! Her face is so small!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.27,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It really is Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.81,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Is she buying chocolate here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.02,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan loves the chocolate here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:24.15,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big hit among my model friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.32,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.90,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same kind as Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.82,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.82,TD_2nd,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.90,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You really can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.49,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.36,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.82,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.53,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:37.29,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.29,TD_Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.41,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:41.75,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:45.46,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You really like chasing after people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.17,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You have potential as a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.13,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.51,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to like running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.59,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Not just from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.18,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,But from a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.81,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:02.02,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I've never ever thought it'd be better if you weren't around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:02.81,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,If you left...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.94,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone would be really disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone really likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.40,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.36,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.70,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.16,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.41,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.21,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Taiga's having a tough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:25.79,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.05,TD_Thoughts,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.80,TD_Thoughts,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it wasn't everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:37.22,TD_Thoughts,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I didn't get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.10,TD_Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.64,TD_Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'll count on you tomorrow too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:47.06,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,We hit our target, so you didn't have to buy the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.48,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, they're thank you gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.27,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.78,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,For all the people who helped me on the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:58.37,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Like Kitamura-kun, Minorin, and Stupid Chihuahua, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.87,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:05.58,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I gave you chocolate, do you think you would be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:08.08,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.71,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,W-What don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:15.55,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of guy would I be if I wasn't happy about getting chocolate from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.64,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:18.76,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:23.02,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Just giving them to you as-is isn't that nice, so I'll try to make something with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:28.23,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I hope everyone likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.32,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.11,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're already going to the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.28,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I'm fine, just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:40.07,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to thank Taiga-chan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.01,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:59.72,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to pull, calling us all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.76,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.18,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some homemade chocolate to show my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.98,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.69,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.56,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,It seems too important to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:14.40,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the chocolate you were selling yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.11,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten really good at telling lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.15,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:21.24,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wrapping is important, so I reused it, but everything inside is handmade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.99,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.91,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.75,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.08,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday was an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.71,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:34.09,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you went to help save me during the school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.17,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:37.63,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this, all formal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:41.47,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in trouble, Minorin will always come to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.22,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.72,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.77,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You too, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:50.14,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it with Yacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.48,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And, Kitamura-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:58.28,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the one that came out the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.36,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.53,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:04.37,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that carried me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.79,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I haven't told Kushieda yet—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.38,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Were the whites of my eyes showing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:17.46,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what was going to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:20.22,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I rolled down, and there were all these noises around my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.68,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Fainting feels like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.76,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It was like being in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:28.85,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I said a lot of incredible things, like I was half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.85,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up, I was really panicked...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:34.36,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.11,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.07,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.44,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.61,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:43.11,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way! Anyway, it was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.03,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.78,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It was something that no one should hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.70,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If someone heard it, I'd be done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:52.33,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's a really awful thing, I wouldn't be able to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.42,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.71,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.67,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I didn't hear anything, right, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:01.63,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,No one heard anything, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.43,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.60,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Planning on just leaving it with "I didn't hear anything"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.77,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:15.77,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.94,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Are you also okay with no one else hearing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.19,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.32,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,But he couldn't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.28,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The reason lies in the words you're trying to hide, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.87,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.03,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you just say this one thing, this one thing honestly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.62,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.71,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.34,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What an awful face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.84,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Chihuahua...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.76,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.56,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay with you to let Aisaka run away from here this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.26,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.18,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.23,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.90,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.77,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It's Minorin, your best friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.44,TD_2nd,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:59.77,TD_2nd,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:01.32,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You said you like me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.53,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Then believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.45,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, let go, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.28,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:13.16,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you're not the kind of person to blame others for your weakness, wanting something that Minorin wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.62,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Or were you that kind of person after all!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.50,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.59,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.88,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The Minorin I love so much to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.72,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you kidding!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.51,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,My happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:30.43,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Can only be made with my hands, and only with these hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:34.68,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone else decide what I need to be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.48,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as we can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:42.82,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:46.90,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:48.86,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Ami, you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:50.70,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Need to chase after her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.37,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,People who want to, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.46,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, I'm going to chase after Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:59.17,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.00,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:02.75,TD_Thoughts,RYuji,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:05.09,TD_Thoughts,RYuji,0000,0000,0000,,Chase her, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:07.93,TD_Thoughts,RYuji,0000,0000,0000,,Find out how Taiga feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.39,TD_Thoughts,RYuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:14.02,TD_Thoughts,RYuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga's trying so hard to hide it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:16.02,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:36.64,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.14,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's going to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.73,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I left the laundry outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:42.10,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Not just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.90,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I think I left a lot of things hanging out.
